             Welcome to the TMI conference centre.

This file tries to give some general help and information
useful for people new to TMI's conferences.

Anyone permitted by the conveners may participate in meetings.
If you wish to be able to vote on behalf of a group, you should
ask a convener to register you.

"help conf.current" gives information on the current conference,
such as where to find the agenda, when it is being held and who is
convening it.

"help conf.rules" gives the simplified version of Robert's Rules of Order
that the meeting rooms run under.

"help non-lp" gives help for those not used to LPmud command syntax
     
